Package: jless
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libxcb1, libxcb-render0, libxcb-shape0, libxcb-xfixes0
Description: jless is a command-line JSON viewer. Use it as a
 replacement for whatever combination of less, jq, cat and your editor
 you currently use for viewing JSON files. It is written in Rust and
 can be installed as a single standalone binary.
